quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  20,55,"Kuwo lowo (umhlaba) Sadala nina, yaye kuwo apho Siza kunibuyisela, Size Siphinde Sinikhuphe kwakhona"
  20,56,"Inene Thina Sambonisa (uFir’awn) yonke imiqondiso yethu, kodwa waphika, wala"
  20,57,"Yena (uFir’awn) wathi: “Ingaba wena uze kusikhupha elizweni lethu ngemilingo yakho kusini na Mûsâ"
  20,58,"Inene thina siya kukuvezela imilingo efana naleyo; Ngoko ke tyumbani usuku lwendibano phakathi kwenu nathi, olo kungekho namnye kuthi okanye nina oza kusilela ukulugcina, kube kwindawo ephangaleleyo apho omabini (amacala) aza kuba namathuba alinganayo (nabantu babone kakuhle bonke)"
  20,59,"(UMûsâ) wathi: “Indibano yenu iya kuba yimini yomsitho, abantu mababuthelane ndawonye ke ukuphuma kwelanga.”"
  20,60,Ke kaloku uFir’awn wemka waqulunqa icebo waphinda wabuya
  20,61,"(UMûsâ) wathi kubo: “Yeha kuni! Ningaqambi buxoki ngoAllâh, hleze Anitshabalalise nya ngesohlwayo. Yaye inene, lowo uqamba ubuxoki (ngoAllâh), akayi kuphumelela, tu.”"
  20,62,"Emva koko baxoxa phakathi kwabo mayela nabaza kukwenza, baza bayigcina loo ncoko yabo iyimfihlo"
  20,63,"Bathi:“Ineneaba(uMûsânomntakwabo) ngabenzibemilingo. Injongo yabo kukunikhupha ezweni lenu ngemilingo, boyise iinkosi zenu nabahlonitshwa benu.”"
  20,64,"Ngoko ke qulunqani icebo lenu, nibuthelane ndawonye nikrele ngokomgca. Ke kaloku owoyisileyo namhlanje inene yena uya kuba uphumelele.”"
  20,65,"Bathi bona: “Hini na Mûsâ! Mayibe nguwe na oza kuqala ajule okanye ibe sithi abajula kuqala kusini na?”"
  20,66,"UMûsâ wathi: “Nakanye, qalani nina nijule!” Emva koko; nazo iintambo zabo neentonga zabo, ngomlingo, zibonakala kuye (uMoses) ngathi ziyanyakaza ngokukhawuleza"
  20,67,Ke kaloku waziva enoloyiko uMûsâ phakathi kuye
  20,68,"Thina (Allâh) Sathi: “Musa ukoyika! Inene wena uza kuba ngentla kunabo"
  20,69,"Jula ke loo nto isesandleni sakho sokunene! Iza kukuginya (konke) oko bakwenzileyo. Inene oko bakwenzileyo bona yintonga yomenzi wemilingo kuphela, ukanti umenzi wemilingo akasokuze aphumelele naphi na apho akhoyo.”"
  20,70,"Ke kaloku abenzi bemilingo bawa baqubuda. Bathi: “Sikholiwe thina kwiNkosi kaHârûn noMûsâ.”"
  20,71,"(UFir’awn) wathi: “Nikholwa kuye (uMûsâ) ndinganinikanga mvume. Inene yena yinkokeli yenu enifundise imilingo. Ngoko ke ndiya kuninqumla izandla zenu neenyawo zenu ngokwahlukana kwamacala (isandla sokhohlo nonyawo lokunene), yaye ndiya kunibethelela emithini yesundu. Yaye niya kwazi ngokwenene okokuba ngubani na apha kuthi (uFir’awn) neNkosi kaMûsâ (uAllâh) onokunika uncedo nesohlwayo sanaphakade.”"
  20,72,"Bathi bona: “Asingekhe sikhethe wena ngaphezulu kunoko kufike kuthi kuyimiqondiso ecacileyo nangaphezulu kuloWo Wasidalayo. Ngoko ke wena wisa okuwisayo. Wena ungawisa (isigwebo) kobu bomi balo mhlaba (kuphela)"
  20,73,"Inene thina sikholiwe eNkosini yethu, (ukwenzela) ukuba Isixolele iziphoso zethu, nakwimilingo obusinyanzela yona (ukuba siyenze). Kwaye uAllâh nguYena Ulungileyo nongapheliyo”"
  20,74,Inene lowo uya kuza eNkosini yakhe (uAllâh) esisaphula- mthetho inene okwakhe iya kuba sisiHogo; akayi kufa engayi kuphila apho
  20,75,"Kodwa yena lowo uya kuza kuYe (uAllâh) elikholwa, enze imisebenzi elungileyo okwabanjalo iya kuba sisikhudla esiphezulu"
  20,76,"IMiyezo ekuya kuhlalwa kuyo ngonaphakade, ekumpompoza imilambo ngaphantsi kwayo, apho baza kuhlala khona ngonaphakade. Lowo ke ngumvuzo walowo uzihlambululayo"
  20,77,"Kananjalo Satyhilela uMûsâ, “Hamba ngobusuku nezicaka zaM, uzibethele indlela eyomileyo enqumla elwandle; akuyi koyika kufunyanwa (nguFir’awn, ungayi koyika kutshona.)”"
  20,78,"Ke kaloku uFir’awn wabaleqa ngemikhosi yakhe, kodwa wona amanzi olwandle abagqumelela"
  20,79,UFir’awn wakhokelela abantu bakhe ekulahlekeni yaye akazanga abanike siKhokelo (silungileyo)
  20,80,"Hini na Bantwana bakwaSirayeli! Sanisindisa elutshabeni lwenu, Saza Senza uMnqophiso nani kwicala langasekunene lentaba. Sanithobela imana nezagwityi"
  20,81,"(Sisithi): “Yidlani kwizinto ezilungileyo, eSinibonelela ngazo ningagabadeli apho, kuba hleze umsindo waM uhle phezu kwenu. Ke lowo uhlelwe yingqumbo yaM phezu kwakhe utshabalele ngenene yena"
  20,82,"Ukanti inene Mna Ndiyaxolela kulowo uguqukayo, akholwe, enze imisebenzi elungileyo aqhubeke (nokuba phantsi) kwesiKhokelo.”"